* Compiling and Building (GHC = 7.4)

$ cabal configure 
$ cabal build 

* If haskell-mpi fails to install then do 

$ cabal unpack 
$ cd to the directry 
$ cabal install --extra-include-dirs=/path/to/mpi/headers --extra-lib-dirs=/usr/lib/openmpi

* To run the parallel merge using 5 processes
* It will sort a list of 100 numbers (from 1 to 100) which was given in reverse 
* order 

$ ./run.sh 5


